aWLI_MixedLifeOrDisabilityProduct.Description:
{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1036{\fonttbl{\f0\fswiss\fprq2\fcharset0 Calibri;}{\f1\fnil MS Sans Serif;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\lang1033\f0\fs22 Term to 100 Life Insurance is a pure term life insurance that provides coverage for as long as you live. The premiums are guaranteed to stay the same for life. After you reach age 100, you will no longer pay premiums; however your coverage will continue until your death. \par
You can choose a coverage amount that suits your needs, and you\rquote re eligible to apply if you are between the ages of 20 and 70.\par
Mixed product: can be subscribed by an individual or a legal entity.\par
When subscribed by a legal entity means that a key person of the company is insured.\par
Note: this product has no term, so is never renewed. Then the rates stay the same in Wynsure.\par
\pard\cf1\lang1036\f1\fs16\par
}

